These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, september
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, 7up
House: art-deco, colonial, palace
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, writer, teacher
1. the musician is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the teacher##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the musician is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the palace house is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Birthday         | october | january   | september   |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | tea | 7up |
| House   | palace  | art-deco    | colonial      |
| Job     | writer     | musician      | teacher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, sudoku
3 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, poker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis, marigold
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, iced-tea
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person drinking water is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Hobby          | board-games  | woodworking     | sudoku     |
| Game   | scrabble     | poker     | canasta      |
| Flower   | marigold  | amaryllis | daisy |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | water     | tea       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, marigold, aconite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, lacrosse
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, bridge
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, train, bus
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the train is the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person driving the bike is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Flower          | azalea  | aconite     | marigold     |
| Sport           | lacrosse | surfing  | parkour   |
| Game   | domino  | backgammon    | bridge |
| Transport           | bus     | bike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, pall-mall, swisher
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, sunflower
City: hannover, san-francisco, paris
House: cape-cod, futuristic, craftsman
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the swisher-smoker is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person traveling to hannover##2
4. the pall-mall-smoker is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar    | bolivar       | swisher  | pall-mall   |
| Flower     | amaryllis    | sunflower  | tulip |
| City     | san-francisco   | paris | hannover        |
| House   | craftsman | cape-cod     | futuristic      |

