.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, australian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dannemann, oliveros
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, horror, western
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, bartender, architect
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the police-officer is between the person watching western movies and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the alhambra-smoker is the bartender##1
4. the canadian is on the right of the australian##1
5. the police-officer is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality          | australian    | canadian     | dutch      |
| Cigar         | alhambra | dannemann | oliveros |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | horror       | romance       |
| Job           | bartender     | police-officer       | architect     |

