.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
House: art-deco, palace, farmhouse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, skateboarding
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, chaman, tiparillo
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the palace house and the chaman-smoker##2
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
5. the art-deco house is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| House          | palace | art-deco | farmhouse    |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | sprite      | 7up |
| Sport   | parkour   | cricket     | skateboarding        |
| Cigar           | bongani      | tiparillo       | chaman      |

