.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, pony, rat
City: colone, new-york, miami
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, poppy
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, lemonade
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the owner of the rat and the person drinking soy-milk##2
3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to miami and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Pet          | rat      | pony   | snake |
| City         | colone | new-york | miami |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | poppy | zinnia   |
| Beverage     | lemonade         | juice  | soy-milk       |

