.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, canasta
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, avocado, pomegranate
House: victorian, ranch-style, futuristic
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, thai, japanese
1. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the thai##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the victorian house is between the person eating avocado and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Game      | bridge       | mah-jongg      | canasta      |
| Food         | avocado    | pomegranate | broccoli      |
| House           | futuristic | victorian     | ranch-style |
| Nationality   | thai     | japanese          | argentine       |

