The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, pop, salsa
1. the fan salsa is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is basketball##2
2. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the cottage house is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the fan pop##1
6. the fan pop is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| House      | cottage      | gothic-revival | futuristic     |
| Color          | chestnut   | pink      | lavender     |
| Sport   | basketball  | tennis      | snowboarding |
| Music-Genre     | blues | salsa        | pop     |

