.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, german, malaysian
City: liverpool, marseilles, hannover
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, writing, woodworking
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, whist
1. the malaysian is between the person playing backgammon and the person traveling to hannover##2
2. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the german##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Nationality      | german    | malaysian          | chinese |
| City          | hannover | marseilles           | liverpool        |
| Hobby           | writing | woodworking | drawing         |
| Game   | mah-jongg    | whist    | backgammon      |

