3 different games are played: whist, chess, billiard
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person playing whist and the person traveling to prague##2
3. the librarian is on the far left##1
4. the blend-smoker is the person playing whist##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the security-guard##1
6. the security-guard is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Job       | librarian | security-guard | bartender |
| City         | prague   | marseilles       | nizza        |
| Cigar       | ritmeester | bongani   | blend         |
| Game   | billiard    | chess     | whist         |

