.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
House: farmhouse, art-deco, futuristic
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, german
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, amber, blue
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, november
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the pakistani is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who likes amber is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is the futuristic house##1
5. the german is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who likes amber##2
6. the person who likes blue is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| House        | art-deco      | farmhouse | futuristic |
| Nationality         | pakistani     | german    | spanish        |
| Color       | amber | blue   | chestnut   |
| Birthday   | august          | february     | november       |

 